   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="discussion">
      <p>
Remarks
</p>
      <p>
         <tp:taxon-name>
Clivotirolites
</tp:taxon-name>
gen. nov.
differs from 
<tp:taxon-name>
Paratirolites
</tp:taxon-name>
and related genera in the oblique protracting outline of the outer suture line.
</p>
